reviewText:
Personally I like these type of games but the focus is definitely on the puzzles in the first place  and then the story. The environment is beautiful but it's not meant for exploring.

Pros:
- nice puzzles, quite relaxing to figure them out, quite on the easy side though;
- beautiful environment;
- fun story for a puzzle game, the stories are useually really bad in this genre so I was positively surprised;

Cons:
- no exploring/very lineair;
- apparently it does not run on every computer (I had no problems, though);
- you play through the game quite quickly.

Games like these are my guilty pleasure. It's a relax mode of adventure.
